query:
SELECT 
  ej.*,
  p.nome as pesquisa_nome
FROM enrichment_jobs ej
LEFT JOIN pesquisas p ON ej.pesquisaId = p.id
WHERE p.projectId = 330001
ORDER BY ej.createdAt DESC
